# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in git.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if delegates have different platforms,
#   you may want to exclude Pipfile.lock.
#   Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similarly, in case of poetry, it's recommended to include poetry.lock in git.
#   poetry.lock

# pdm
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, it is recommended to include pdm.lock in git.
